## üóÇÔ∏è Quick Navigation Guide
### For Different User Types:
#### Complete Beginners (Never Used ADB Before)
**Start Here:**
1. Read: [PlayStore_Toolkit_DOCS.md](PlayStore_Toolkit_DOCS.md) - "Quick Start Guide" section
2. Follow: [Tutorials_Workflows.md](Tutorials_Workflows.md) - "Tutorial 1: First-Time Setup"
3. Reference: [Quick_Reference_Cards.md](Quick_Reference_Cards.md) - "System Master" section
**Estimated Time:** 30 minutes to get started
---
#### Intermediate Users (Have Used ADB, Want Better Performance)
**Start Here:**
1. Skim: [PlayStore_Toolkit_DOCS.md](PlayStore_Toolkit_DOCS.md) - "Core Modules" section
2. Follow: [Tutorials_Workflows.md](Tutorials_Workflows.md) - "Tutorial 2: Gaming Optimization"
3. Keep Open: [Quick_Reference_Cards.md](Quick_Reference_Cards.md) for command reference
**Estimated Time:** 45 minutes to optimize
---
#### Advanced Users (Root Access, Custom ROMs)
**Start Here:**
1. Read: [PlayStore_Toolkit_DOCS.md](PlayStore_Toolkit_DOCS.md) - "Advanced Features" section
2. Experiment: Use `--help` on each script
3. Customize: Modify scripts based on device specifics
4. Reference: [Glossary_Troubleshooting.md](Glossary_Troubleshooting.md) for deep dives
**Estimated Time:** Variable (experimentation)
---
#### Troubleshooting / Problem Solving
**Start Here:**
1. Search: [Glossary_Troubleshooting.md](Glossary_Troubleshooting.md) - "Troubleshooting Database"
2. If not found: [PlayStore_Toolkit_DOCS.md](PlayStore_Toolkit_DOCS.md) - "Troubleshooting" section
3. Still stuck: Check GitHub Issues or Discord support
**Response Time:** Most issues resolved in < 10 minutes
