Total Time: ~50 minutes
```
### Path 2: I Want Better Gaming Performance
```
1. Quick_Reference_Cards.md ‚Üí Gaming Workflow (5 min)
2. Tutorials_Workflows.md ‚Üí Tutorial 2 (45 min)
3. PlayStore_Toolkit_DOCS.md ‚Üí VVIP Optimizer (10 min)
4. Apply optimizations ‚úì
Total Time: ~60 minutes
```
### Path 3: I Have a Specific Problem
```
1. Glossary_Troubleshooting.md ‚Üí Search for error message (2 min)
2. Follow solution steps (5-15 min)
3. If unresolved, check PlayStore_Toolkit_DOCS.md ‚Üí Troubleshooting
4. Problem solved ‚úì
Total Time: ~20 minutes
```
### Path 4: I Want to Understand Everything
```
1. PlayStore_Toolkit_DOCS.md ‚Üí Read entire document (90 min)
2. Glossary_Troubleshooting.md ‚Üí Glossary section (30 min)
3. Quick_Reference_Cards.md ‚Üí All cards (20 min)
