## üìû Support & Community
### Official Channels:
- **GitHub Issues:** https://github.com/SecFerro/toolkit/issues
- **Email Support:** support@secferro.dev
- **Discord Community:** https://discord.gg/secferro
- **XDA Forum:** https://forum.xda-developers.com/...
### Before Asking for Help:
1. ‚úì Check [Glossary_Troubleshooting.md](Glossary_Troubleshooting.md) - 90% of issues covered
2. ‚úì Search GitHub issues for similar problems
3. ‚úì Run `sh script.sh --debug` and save output
4. ‚úì Provide device model, Android version, error message
### Response Times:
- **GitHub Issues:** 24-48 hours
- **Discord:** Real-time (community-driven)
- **Email:** 48-72 hours
- **Emergency (bootloop):** 2-6 hours
